The ingredients: Venti White Chocolate Mocha with 12 shots of espresso, 2 shots of soy, extra whipped cream, toffee syrup, hazelnut syrup, extra Mocha drizzle and extra Caramel drizzle. Caffeine content: 1,150mg (or, the equivalent of 15 Red Bulls). The damage: $14.25 (but really, it was free).

properties.title: Day 916 - Day 186
properties.description: rhome_music posted a photo: Lifetime Dream # 143 of my list of 155: I will create and maintain an autobiography of all of my personal memories that I will be able to pass down to further generations. I lost my last grandparent in June of 2001, my grandmother June. I lost my first grandparent, my father’s mother when I was very young- around 7. My grandfathers died within about 3 years of one another in late 1989 and early 1992. I can remember just about every detail of the deaths of all of my relatives, but I am at a loss to know many of the details of their lives. In fact what I do know about all of them, I learned after they passed away. There is so much history and understanding about them that was just lost. As a lover of History and Genealogy, that makes me all the more sad. I began writing down my memories, categorized by the year that I am writing about. I am including everything that I can remember, from the places I went, the people I met, and the toys I played with. When I can, I include pictures. I want my kids to know everything about me that they possibly can and when I become old and senile- well, I want to remember who I was as well! I have many stories to write out, and I imagine with these stories I will be drinking a lot of coffee. Pictured here is my new Starbucks mug (love the design), and I plan on getting a lot of miles out of it!!
